snippet.title: RollerCoaster Tycoon 3 - PS & Xbox Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
RollerCoaster Tycoon 3: Complete Edition is coming to Xbox and PlayStation! Get ready to build the theme park of your dreams, design jaw-dropping coasters, and manage every aspect of your park like a true tycoon. Are you ready to become the ultimate theme park tycoon?

Pre-Order Today: https://urals.co/atari/rct3-on-console

Join the Atari Discord: https://link.atari.com/atariclubdiscord

Follow Atari
Twitter: https://twitter.com/atari
